<DOC><DOCNO> AP880525-0170 </DOCNO><FILEID>AP-NR-05-25-88 1615EDT</FILEID><FIRST>r i AM-BRF--India-Flood     05-25 0072</FIRST><SECOND>AM-BRF--India-Flood,0074</SECOND><HEAD>13 Dead in Indian Flooding</HEAD><DATELINE>NEW DELHI, India (AP) </DATELINE><TEXT>   Melting snow from the Himalayastriggered flooding that inundated 52 villages, killed 13 people andforced hundreds of families to flee to higher ground, it wasreported Wednesday.   The flooding occurred along the Brahmaputra River and itstributaries in the northeastern state of Assam, the United News ofIndia said.   The river also flooded thousands of acres of farmland.</TEXT></DOC>